History:Laws 1984, ch. 127, § 109; Laws 2000, ch. 61, § 1; 1978 Comp., § 59A-7-3, repealed and reenacted by Laws 2016, ch. 89, § 6; 2017, ch. 58, § 1; 2017, ch. 130, § 5.

